@startuml
|User|
start
: Click on Update button;
|System|
: Display form to update Branch;
|User|
repeat: Input new branch information;
: Click on Confirm button;
|System|
: Validate new information;
backward: Show error message;
repeat while (Information Valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: Update Branch Information;
: Update Manage Branch screen;
stop
@enduml